Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.io.hfile

Interface HFile.Reader

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, Closeable, HFile.CachingBlockReader
All Known Implementing Classes:
HFilePreadReader, HFileReaderImpl, HFileStreamReader
Enclosing class:
HFile
public static interface HFile.Reader extends Closeable, HFile.CachingBlockReader
An interface used by clients to open and iterate an HFile.
